ou calculated those 279ns? 2 cycles per instruction? And where that Phi2 came from? Datasheet?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4892">Duck_tech</a> — Tue Jun 07, 2011 12:51 pm</p><hr />
