<author><name><![CDATA[Duck_tech]]></name></author>
<updated>2011-06-07T10:42:20-07:00</updated>
<published>2011-06-07T10:42:20-07:00</published>
<id>http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=7751&amp;p=79372#p79372</id>
